{"tid":620304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】元朗一處山坡樹林起火 (20:24)","createTime":"2018-04-07T12:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T13:18:30.000Z","uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f6978de9fa32f5b015b2141bb6297a9bbaa038","tid":620304,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"今晚近8時，元朗勝意花園附近一處山坡樹林忽然着火，有途人發現立即報警。火勢尚未太猛時，已有消防陸續趕抵現場，10分鐘後將火救熄。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">距離今次火場有一段距離的元朗南生圍，近一個月接連發生至少4宗懷疑縱火案</span>，包括2日（星期一）清晨6時許，橫水渡碼頭部分及一艘橫水渡木船被焚毀，警方暫列縱火案跟進，並曾在現場進行問卷調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180407/s00001/1523103916290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180407%2Fs00001%2F1523103916290&d=xofnaCHj%2BqiTBLGoIczafl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=24b1f294\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180407%2Fs00001%2F1523103916290&h=20c97a8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180407/s00001/1523103916290</a>"},{"pid":"856bf0783464e93379920aa9c247a14d06aeddff","tid":620304,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"田生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1ce5d65f9fdbcf6ad309ab3b3564f3fdd3129c","tid":620304,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3b5cbde10a1fb0337482c669bd76a593977f75","tid":620304,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"消防員加油<br />\n呢排無得抖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw多謝縱火者為我地爭取裸照福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f67735e1e3